---
title: Italian-Seasoned Salmon with Baked Orzo
description: Ciao bella! This light and delicious meal spotlights Italian-seasoned salmon – but the accompanying side could steal the show; creamy orzo is topped with zucchini and Parmesan and baked to dreamy perfection. Pour the wine and set the table!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-a-litalienne-99947c08.jpg
